data.name: labelStart.Text
data.value: We are ready to install Mayfly software on your PC. This wizard will pass you through the setup process. Click 'Next' to read license agreement.

data.name: label1.Text
data.value: Select prodict you want to download and install then click 'Next' to proceed with End User Agreement.

data.name: labelEula.Text
data.value: Read license agreement carefully. Click 'Agree' button if you agree all the statements or click 'Cancel' if you don't.

data.name: label4.Text
data.value: Select user interface language then click 'Next' to proceed with installation.

data.name: labelLangInstruction.Text
data.value: Please, type your name in the field below. It will be used in all of your data cards further. It should be the same as what you will specify purchasing additional features.

data.name: checkBoxOptions.Text
data.value: I want to see all installation options

data.name: labelShortcutInstruction.Text
data.value: Select where you want to create shortcuts. We recommend to place it at least in Start menu.

data.name: labelFileTypeExists.Text
data.value: Also select action on already existing file type associations.

data.name: labelFileTypes.Text
data.value: Select if you want to register new file types and its property handlers.

data.name: labelDone.Text
data.value: Now we are done with installing Mayfly software on your PC. You may start to use software.
